{"tid":1581994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日日都連登神探 其他活動post沉曬","createTime":"2019-09-20T00:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T11:37:07.000Z","uid":50457,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"00a4242810bf8e33e08622a9b07fafc219a9373d","tid":1581994,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T00:25:22.000Z","msg":"最近兩星期的活動post沉曬，係因為日日都連登神探洗版<br />\n<br />\n邊度邊度死人同831有關<br />\n個度個度死者有可以，同新屋嶺有關<br />\n邊個邊個有通靈能力，見到義士<br />\n邊個朋友消失左，大家快搵<br />\n<br />\n仲要成班人樂此不疲,日日特登搵呢啲新聞或自己作的神探推理post洗版<br />\n<br />\n老老實實，個啲咩<br />\n(核彈！有圖！)(細絲極恐！)呢類post10個有9個都係誇張失實，出post的穿鑿附會的推理，一來既不嚴謹，二來浪費大家精神<br />\n<br />\n我想問，呢類神探post對呢場運動，對連登作為行動重要平台，有咩幫助？係無啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你打得贏呢場運動，咩cctv都會攞到，打唔贏的話就唔係一次721,831,新屋嶺，<span style=\"color: red;\">而係每一日721,831,新屋嶺</span><br />\n<br />\n行動post沉曬，呢班連登神探比五毛的破壞力更驚人，希望大家唔好再推個啲咩死人有可疑，失蹤，怪聲的post。<br />\n<br />\n助長垃圾post吸引大家注意，大家慢慢就唔會再入連登，活動就散晒"},{"pid":"72b0217a04d45defe998999088d26b303c308176","tid":1581994,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T00:25:55.000Z","msg":"[公海 文宣整合] 9.29全球反極權集會 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581746</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2FUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=bd07905a\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2FUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=88d3dd3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ</a>"},{"pid":"110c07ae5f7a7e5d4bcbfe5826e96d554aa35617","tid":1581994,"uid":85425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T00:29:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e22c949c120dbbd4c93d25d80ca0657b1b9efa1","tid":1581994,"uid":120151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T00:31:44.000Z","msg":"！"},{"pid":"241f8d12c0266c942fb111858d4b3995bddaf070","tid":1581994,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T00:35:20.000Z","msg":"個個去曬查案 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b393ce8e76b992d6b500cfd6d12ff85182c722","tid":1581994,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T00:36:41.000Z","msg":"當日血傘運動中後期，高登時事台情況類似，唔係日日神探post,但係日日分化post<br />\n<br />\n由於中共網軍分法唔到大家，而家就帶動一股散播神秘死亡新聞，令大家對此樂此不疲<br />\n<br />\n目的永遠如一：將大家視線，由對中共的憤怒轉為對虛擬示威者的同情<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個星期係關鍵，讓所有呢類垃圾post沉落去，運動就可以再燒起來"},{"pid":"52f5d2b0de3d72fcb82c8376baaeb737e5c9ba7b","tid":1581994,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T00:38:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98a7da2743ebdbb712d4d128014628fe2fb45697","tid":1581994,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T00:45:34.000Z","msg":"神探永遠只在晚上活動"},{"pid":"da6d6228a37cdcddf3a4e20868ef3e819515056c","tid":1581994,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T00:47:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b641fd19698b02d8eab1419359a8e9be2d2826c6","tid":1581994,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T00:49:10.000Z","msg":"同意"